<body>
    <h1>20260526 - RRP Touchpoint</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h2 local-id=3D"4b50eb0aef69" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-1.Key=
Decisions">1. Key Decisions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"9db51b32-6344-4a07-8849-0f863ee75369">
<li local-id=3D"7c4a2a9d-b497-48c2-9852-62fcdf7ae0c2">
<p local-id=3D"0c58be7500cc"><strong>Standard Template Mandatory</strong></=
p>
<ul local-id=3D"3c994ede-86cd-4309-9c1d-9b20fc6fc432">
<li local-id=3D"edccf3d7-ce25-4e3e-bc86-c8cee727f4fb">
<p local-id=3D"2b27471842e4">All Rapid Recovery Plans (RRP) must use the ap=
proved template.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8da34868-0ef4-4230-98e7-3dd26781e7df">
<p local-id=3D"224e4a06fc37">Template includes: triage steps, recovery sequ=
ences, and scenario-based documentation.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"01a2930c-67fa-4a27-981d-75f7c0982caf">
<p local-id=3D"5d926d1e5ad8"><strong>Scenario-Based Documentation Model Ado=
pted</strong><br>
Each application must document 3 scenario types:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"b962bfdf-00f2-41ae-92a2-7de8901fd3bc">
<li local-id=3D"42b52493-3b91-401a-bcf6-d20501a62e8b">
<p local-id=3D"63ad0d75fbf5">Restart-based recovery</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1ac220f2-9a9b-4c58-b84e-8e920bc6dd68">
<p local-id=3D"825e0e7e8042">Workaround + restart</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"405bc37f-6aa2-4bb2-9a6f-758b5f00e39a">
<p local-id=3D"23d823c1a3e7">Non-restart (e.g., data correction)</p></li>
</ol></li>
<li local-id=3D"f9765345-434a-417e-8a8a-0381e1df4787">
<p local-id=3D"2575c94bbffd"><strong>Controlled Publishing Process</strong>=
</p>
<ul local-id=3D"208367e9-ba44-479e-b1b8-e16000b8e30d">
<li local-id=3D"8bc28ad0-178c-48ea-8d5e-4d354100400c">
<p local-id=3D"82b8a2968ed2">No self-publishing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f5e4a790-39e8-4af5-9728-3ceb5d1743be">
<p local-id=3D"cdd7f326abe0">All RRPs must be <strong>submitted to Thabani =
for validation and KB publishing</strong>.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"72e292c5-a360-4961-b098-53a592a7270a">
<p local-id=3D"3f63f15081d9">RRPs are <strong>living documents</strong> (co=
ntinuous updates expected).</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"9bb64203-e3ee-4b02-8988-f0c6b3679a24">
<h2 local-id=3D"ecbcefdb42df" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-2.Priority&am=
p;Timeline(Critical)">2. Priority &amp; Timeline (Critical)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"d71d2a91-2a81-46a7-8b32-c4da61f65663">
<li local-id=3D"b9e3d9ab-73e0-49c8-8181-7b8d93a8aad8">
<p local-id=3D"891151905a18"><strong>Scope:</strong> 6 Gold Applications (r=
egulatory priority)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"32910565-0c83-48d9-a01d-165d2e76a321">
<p local-id=3D"e61f9264b89a"><strong>June 10:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2264c70e-af29-4d01-95be-d0e4db66a76d">
<li local-id=3D"7657a30b-ae30-49a4-ad45-8e793172fda4">
<p local-id=3D"3bd5895064a9">Reboot / restart sequences completed for all 6=
 apps</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f8264f6-d120-4bef-8a67-fec5f9da3f1f">
<p local-id=3D"610da21f086d"><strong>June 30:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"38ec0ca7-79cc-4f42-a8f3-d104b9a07125">
<li local-id=3D"80ebb8da-0445-4bfe-8eb1-66d2196cfb42">
<p local-id=3D"7a8d331884b2">Full RRP completion (audit-ready)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0f07aff45e2f">=E2=9A=A0=EF=B8=8F Gold apps currently <strong=
>not fully compliant</strong> with architecture standards<br>
(local redundancy, LB, DR) =E2=86=92 remediation planned separately</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c698ce35-b6c1-44ac-8030-73de1d925ab2">
<h2 local-id=3D"6e58338fdde1" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-3.ExecutionAp=
proach">3. Execution Approach</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"11972801e229" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-A.Application=
OnboardingStrategy">A. Application Onboarding Strategy</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"3edf07ad-d3fb-4679-bd23-582a5b952507">
<li local-id=3D"ed5e6ec3-dba1-4668-aa6c-0103e484ead7">
<p local-id=3D"a7fe2fc8a5af">Prioritize:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e031e960-b130-495c-806b-766f3622f09e">
<li local-id=3D"4ab56efb-19bd-44be-a185-78c82358d6ca">
<p local-id=3D"5898b87568a9">Apps with <strong>recent major incidents</stro=
ng> (faster stakeholder engagement)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"88cff50c-4780-4d30-aee0-1152281bc1b3">
<p local-id=3D"0db8e3b48ec7"><strong>Easier apps first</strong> for momentu=
m</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc8e11e1-3d54-43d5-90fc-0567ec0894d0">
<p local-id=3D"b6f43e4eefed">Parallel track:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"23e31440-5d95-47c5-a41b-0f1faa097a54">
<li local-id=3D"780bc29d-1231-4f90-8452-b6e1f8c28e14">
<p local-id=3D"d4bde3ce7468">Begin coverage for <strong>all in-scope applic=
ations</strong></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"8ad37d31a4eb" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-B.BaselineSta=
ndardization">B. Baseline Standardization</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"1bf3bc03-6b4c-432a-a780-3ed7efcd8dee">
<li local-id=3D"d09f1781-4825-44f0-8578-2f30abb9175f">
<p local-id=3D"a19c7a64913e"><strong>Mandatory integration of restart runbo=
oks</strong><br>
(source: Kanagaraj=E2=80=99s team)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"369b81be-4966-4050-9fb0-4de879d12968">
<p local-id=3D"1c96e51ff042">Use:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4acd8685-a19b-45ea-99f7-1280417d328e">
<li local-id=3D"684529ac-d192-4a43-8c20-e36ed4e5f056">
<p local-id=3D"351b92a4165c">Existing <strong>incident analysis for Gold ap=
ps</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"412ddd80-ab6c-4cd2-90ae-09d2f148e554">
<p local-id=3D"6ca766a6bfc1">Identify restart-resolvable failure patterns</=
p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"f55213dd-11d6-460d-8620-a7a1456791df">
<h2 local-id=3D"8186044af56a" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-4.KnowledgeBa=
se&amp;Compliance">4. Knowledge Base &amp; Compliance</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"f7de5b1f-a2b1-42d9-abe0-7b4e5740364e">
<li local-id=3D"93897c23-e1df-4014-9e27-cd90f1542ed4">
<p local-id=3D"492342435896">RRPs linked via <strong>PEM Link to CIs</stron=
g> in Knowledge Base</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5bbe482e-7279-4846-bbc0-8345d5fc0f18">
<p local-id=3D"d88709b0e976">Mandatory for:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7f2b8001-ca10-4c1f-9bfe-0de444a766fe">
<li local-id=3D"e1a2384d-f901-4205-91e8-72960ac0fa80">
<p local-id=3D"344389e3ab3e"><strong>All Gold applications (current regulat=
ory requirement)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7daf855b-6203-494d-8d33-8d24c1fa9125">
<p local-id=3D"ba0d0f6bd97e">Future: <strong>all applications</strong></p><=
/li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"abc2f853-ecbf-4f97-8bc6-d4606df85294">
<p local-id=3D"0be11d4da324"><strong>Production readiness gate:</strong></p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"27a824be-546d-4153-bc7f-60cc7647970b">
<li local-id=3D"bea01eee-7631-4a74-916e-2c7e790131e1">
<p local-id=3D"cb317e5d95a6">RRP + SRD + DR required before go-live (Infra =
intake process)</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8f13e38c-9779-42c4-9e20-4c69b910aa18">
<h2 local-id=3D"5b760613ee14" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-5.OperatingMo=
del(GOCC&amp;ITSMIntegration)">5. Operating Model (GOCC &amp; ITSM Integrat=
ion)</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"74561827-de25-49d1-b820-9a68f0875e36">
<li local-id=3D"b4613e63-9788-49de-96d7-1325abd562c8">
<p local-id=3D"e824a7d6aecd"><strong>GOCC (George / Jonan team)</strong></p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"8e858bd1-1196-4185-9fb0-c370a607ef50">
<li local-id=3D"b5e5705c-2b53-49f4-b41e-06e5b8e98869">
<p local-id=3D"88174b4d5950">Acts as extension of app support</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8dfdb617-cdf4-4a1f-8368-9b4b6a09eccb">
<p local-id=3D"c122c366d58d">Drives triage speed and execution during incid=
ents</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"9b1854ec-bb1a-41d5-8b8a-529cece863c0">
<p local-id=3D"bf460dec7e51"><strong>ITSM Integration (Confirmed)</strong><=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"af882f75-fff4-43bf-90da-d294c1c8d3c9">
<li local-id=3D"0e7e8228-83d7-4f1a-b1b7-61fd55db1045">
<p local-id=3D"8933458e33fd">Post-incident: =E2=86=92 RRP updates will be t=
riggered via Incident/Problem Management</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fee3cf06-eb64-4899-bd3d-ebf972e7e029">
<p local-id=3D"83e982d5ba53">Ownership: =E2=86=92 Rohina team covers Proble=
m + Change alignment</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6b83be56-48df-4d27-8914-8fc1fd8acab6">
<h2 local-id=3D"7a73d342749d" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-6.Clarificati=
onsonTemplateUsage">6. Clarifications on Template Usage</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"8fccb73e-75f2-43b9-b3e3-7dc3129eac02">
<li local-id=3D"04cb55ca-0158-46a4-a102-35141b62d284">
<p local-id=3D"13c5af6dc336">Template questions =3D <strong>guidance, not y=
es/no</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff4171b7-b1fc-4d74-bf55-cfdb9fda37cd">
<p local-id=3D"269b27db3a22">Expected input:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3546a978-dc4e-4f31-9d66-681db6ccfb0a">
<li local-id=3D"c14fa937-2b41-4700-8d54-8b2b76220870">
<p local-id=3D"e585d0fc0b5a">Detailed, descriptive operational steps</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"b0bb9bbf-fa1d-4d81-bd69-74c516a19322">
<p local-id=3D"9a1990ada98c">Explicit configs, sequences, and recovery logi=
c</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b2176897-6f4f-4239-af7f-5a4e19fe347f">
<h2 local-id=3D"468ffcd8ebbf" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-7.Risks/Const=
raints">7. Risks / Constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"67c1d200-4a4a-414b-be54-59cadae6cad7">
<li local-id=3D"e1df0e53-b5bd-4022-b45a-6373cb2ef1f0">
<p local-id=3D"a596f4db21d2">Gold app architecture gaps (DR, redundancy)</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"208dc0c3-b815-4e85-91e9-fdec7fba11cb">
<p local-id=3D"c361ef466c47">Dependency on:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4b3818c0-715e-49b6-9b93-6e8c5af9daff">
<li local-id=3D"30108a97-27e7-43e5-a644-1d15e979d4e4">
<p local-id=3D"983f99bf0bbb">Restart runbooks (Kanagaraj team)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"04cdbee5-ae89-4645-8171-049678b1d747">
<p local-id=3D"b7def8fc1e22">Timely validation (Thabani bottleneck risk)</p=
></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"550b0d2d-ba2e-4d4f-9d4c-15d53539930e">
<p local-id=3D"2042d1be5123">Tight timeline (June 10 milestone)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"47e6e45b-1370-4c35-b381-1a1f767b32d9">
<h1 local-id=3D"51f10178838a" id=3D"id-20260526-RRPTouchpoint-8.ActionTrack=
er(ClearOwnership)">8. Action Tracker (Clear Ownership)</h1>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"760" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"1e=
4f3018-3e02-40c7-89fa-9844acd4097d" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"7d1e9344-9d14-406d-a81b-7fc074670699">
<th data-local-id=3D"584a9875-6125-43bb-b204-bebf4de38a5d" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"32a9ff95a98f">Action</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"046ead05-56ea-49d4-b78d-a2839a81cc53" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"51cecd7fbf20">Owner</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"25e4e7da-095a-49a0-ae98-b303fbb57241" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"4a3dcf99e7ed">Due</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"5c665471-00b6-474e-8c52-116b3b73a328" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"e7171cab8b81">Notes</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"fcb57a1b-2815-4d80-be0b-ac85bb212233">
<td data-local-id=3D"0469f38c-3142-478e-96a5-61f6febe59f1" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"ed7b51c998c5">Complete RRP using template (all scenarios)</p=
></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"eb838b7d-060b-4502-867a-f35c535b8128" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"8aec6c2332a3">Balaji, Prabu</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"b95d15b6-420e-4b69-9d58-fc2525625687" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6d09c6079bb8">Ongoing</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"807a6d7d-4e04-42be-8701-737d5a1a9bc8" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"2250c8192675">Submit per app</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"d85a1395-d56e-4eda-86cc-f25c885706cf">
